#BCD formt
# the BCD stores the Boot Configuration Data in cleartext form
# section names are in square brackets followed by an optional W that marks the section as writable
# a entry is defined as a line containing a colon. they must follow the following format
# type "key" colon "value"
#there are no spaces allowed outside the quotes 
# empty lines are not allowed
# a comment is defined as a newline followed by a hash symbol
#colons and square brackets are not allowed in comments